Reviews were mixed.  While ''[[Sinclair User]]'' only gave the game 6/10,<ref name="SU_Review" /> ''[[CRASH (magazine)|CRASH]]'' awarded it a CRASH Smash at 90%.<ref name="CRASH_Review" />

''Sinclair User'' said of the game "the controls are difficult to handle and of the type where you lose position rapidly through having to over-correct continually",<ref name="SU_Review" /> while ''CRASH'' decided that "the display is wonderful, the best three dimensional [[Battlezone (1980 video game)|Battlezone]]-type game yet... Really excellent, most playable and addictive too."<ref name="CRASH_Review" />

